Scenario         	                         Can You Send to HubSpot?                            	Notes
Basic fields (name, email, phone, etc.)	         âœ… Yes	                                      These map directly to HubSpot CRM contact fields.
Custom fields (like userType, preferences)	    âœ… Yes	                                 You must first create custom properties in HubSpot.
Sensitive data (like password)	              âŒ No	                                           Never send passwords or highly sensitive info. HubSpot is not meant for that.
Long form content (e.g., feedback, messages)	    âœ… Yes	                                 You can send it as a note, timeline event, or custom property.










